## Summary

**Completed: [P0] COMP005 - Build List.Dropdown component (search bar filter)**

### What was done:
- **Created `SearchDropdown` component** (`search_dropdown.tsx`, `search_dropdown.scss`) — a reusable dropdown selector with:
  - Sections support with optional titles and separators
  - Full keyboard navigation (ArrowUp/Down, Enter to select, Escape/Tab to close)
  - Click-outside dismiss
  - Check icon for currently selected option
  - Chevron rotation animation on trigger
  - Proper ARIA: `listbox` role, `option` role on `<div>` elements, `aria-selected`, `aria-activedescendant`, `useId()` for unique IDs, `aria-label` on trigger
- **Updated `SearchBar`** — added optional `dropdown` ReactNode prop, rendered after the input
- **Wired demo in `App.tsx`** — filter by All/Commands/Applications in root search view
- **Tokenized all values** — `$search-dropdown-trigger-height`, `$search-dropdown-menu-min-width`, `$search-dropdown-menu-max-height`, `$z-dropdown`, `$z-search-dropdown`
- **Updated `actions_dropdown.scss`** to use `$z-dropdown` token for consistency
- All 93 tests pass, `bun run check` passes

